Description_lang: Divine Storm, Divine Hammer and Consecration now deal Radiant damage and your abilities that deal Radiant damage deal $s2% increased damage.

description_blz.en_US: Divine Storm, Divine Hammer and Consecration now deal Radiant damage and your abilities that deal Radiant damage deal 5% increased damage.
description_blz.es_MX: Tormenta divina, Martillo divino y Consagración ahora infligen daño radiante, y tus habilidades que infligen daño radiante infligen un 5% más de daño.
description_blz.pt_BR: Tempestade Divina, Martelo Divino e Consagração agora causam dano Radiante, e suas habilidades que causam dano Radiante causam 5% a mais de dano.
description_blz.de_DE: 'Göttlicher Sturm', 'Göttlicher Hammer' und 'Weihe' verursachen nun Strahlenschaden und Eure Strahlenschaden verursachenden Fähigkeiten verursachen 5% mehr Schaden.
description_blz.en_GB: Divine Storm, Divine Hammer and Consecration now deal Radiant damage and your abilities that deal Radiant damage deal 5% increased damage.
description_blz.es_ES: Ahora, Tormenta divina, Martillo divino y Consagración infligen daño Radiante, y tus facultades que causan daño Radiante infligen un 5% más.
description_blz.fr_FR: Tempête Divine, Marteau divin et Consécration infligent désormais des dégâts de rayonnement. Les dégâts des techniques infligeant des dégâts de rayonnement sont augmentés de 5 %.
description_blz.it_IT: Tempesta Divina, Martello Divino e Consacrazione infliggono danni da radiosità, e le tue abilità che infliggono danni da radiosità infliggono il 5% di danni aggiuntivi.
description_blz.ru_RU: "Божественная буря", "Божественный молот" и "Освящение" теперь наносят урон от сияния. Способности, которые наносят урон от сияния, наносят на 5% больше урона.
description_blz.ko_KR: 천상의 폭풍, 천상의 망치, 신성화가 광휘 피해를 입힙니다. 추가로 광휘 피해를 입히는 능력의 공격력이 5%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 神性風暴、神聖之錘和奉獻現在會造成聖輝傷害，且聖輝傷害技能造成的傷害提高5%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 神圣风暴、神圣之锤和奉献现在造成光辉伤害，而且你造成光辉伤害的技能的伤害提高5%。
